    <meta name="citation_reference" content="Steele, M., Morley, R., and Ermold, W.: PHC: A Global Ocean Hydrography with a High-Quality Arctic Ocean, J. Climate, 14, 2079–2087,
https://doi.org/10.1175/1520-0442(2001)014&amp;lt;2079:pagohw&amp;gt;2.0.co;2, 2001. a">
