al.</a> (<a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx50" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">2001</a>)</span><span class="cit" id="xref_text.56"><a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx59" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">Zhang and Rothrock</a> (<a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx59" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">2003</a>)</span><span class="cit" id="xref_text.57"><a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx44" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">O'Dell et al.</a> (<a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx44" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">2008</a>)</span><span class="cit" id="xref_text.58"><a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx36" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">Locarnini et al.</a> (<a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/#bib1.bibx36" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">2013</a>)</span></span><div class="table-wrap splitted" id="Ch1.T5"><div class="caption"><p id="d1e3972"><strong class="caption-number">Table 3</strong>List of the observational and reanalysis datasets for which
a CMORizing script is available in ESMValTool v2.0, together with the
corresponding variables (realms), tier level and reference.</p></div><a class="table-link" href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/gmd-13-1179-2020-t03-web.png" target="_blank"><img src="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/gmd-13-1179-2020-t03-thumb.png" target="_blank" data-webversion="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/gmd-13-1179-2020-t03-web.png" data-width="2067" data-height="4381" data-csvversion="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/gmd-13-1179-2020-t03.xlsx"></a><p class="downloads"><a class="triangle journal-contentLinkColor table-download" href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/1179/2020/gmd-13-1179-2020-t03.xlsx" target="_blank">Download XLSX</a></p></div>



